Bienvenue dans le projet Roadside Assistance - RSA

RSA247 is the culmination of the vision of its creators to provide a carefree and complete road experience for Indian motorists. The personal experiences of on-road services and observations across the country have made RSA247’s creators realize a fact that the currently available roadside assistance has a lot of limitations in serviceability and distance. This realization has planted the seed for RSA247. To create a one-stop solution for all on-road needs of a motorist.
